Class Summary
AbstractFilenameComposite The file name is parsed into a composite with this class as the base composite class.
FilenameDelimiter This class is a composite subclass which represents a delimiter within a filename.
FilenameDelimiterIterator This class is an iterator for the FilenameDelimiter class.
FilenameEndWordDelimiter This class is a delimiter which remains a part of the token, located at the end.
FilenameParenthesis This composite subclass is for parenthesis elements.
FilenameParenthesisIterator This class is an iterator for the FilenameParenthesis class.
FilenameStartWordDelimiter This class is a delimiter which remains a part of the token, located at the start.
FilenameTag This class represents the filename.
FilenameTagBuilder This class builds a FilenameTag.
FilenameToken This composite subclass is the leaf of the tree.
FilenameTokenIterator This class is an iterator for the FilenameToken class.
